data.title: Samsung Galaxy S6 - Specifications
data.meta_description: Specifications of the Samsung Galaxy S6. Dimensions: 70.5 x 143.4 x 6.8 mm, Weight: 138 g, SoC: Samsung Exynos 7 Octa 7420, CPU: 4x 2.1 GHz ARM Cortex-A57, 4x 1.5 GHz ARM Cortex-A53, GPU: ARM Mali-T760 MP8, 772 MHz, RAM: 3 GB, 1552 MHz, Storage: 32 GB, 64 GB, 128 GB, Display: 5.1 in, Super AMOLED, 1440 x 2560 pixels, 24 bit, Battery: 2550 mAh, Li-Ion, OS: Android 5.0.2 Lollipop. Samsung Galaxy S6 is also known as Samsung SM-G920A, Samsung G920A, Samsung SM-G920F, Samsung G920F, Samsung SM-G920S, Samsung G920S, Samsung SM-G920T, Samsung G920T, Samsung SM-G9200, Samsung G9200, Samsung SM-G9208, Samsung G9208.
